version_description: The original is played by a string quartet plus the voice. I've tried to put some simple guitar chords that work well with the meloy tring to be faithfull to the strings arrangement.
Includes all the rhythm guitar parts, Simple easy to read chords.

"Never Say Die" is a song by English rock band Black Sabbath. It is the title track from their 1978 album of the same name. It was their first UK single to chart since "Paranoid" in 1970, peaking at 21. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D3-hNMqmKK0.
